34  void ChannelDescriptor::Queue(double v, double t) {
35  double delta = t - mNextTime;
36 
37  if (delta > .5 * mRate) {
38 
39  LogDebug(2, "Data loss. Added exception. t=%.18g mNextTime=%.18g delta=%.18g mRate/2=%.18g",
40  t,
41  mNextTime,
42  delta,
43  .5 * mRate);
44 
45  std::stringstream s;
46  s << "Data loss in channel " << mId << ". From t=" << mNextTime << " to t=" << t;
47  mFIS->AddException(s.str(), mNextTime, t, mId);
48 
49  mExceptions.push_back(DataException(mNextTime, t, DataException::data_loss));
50  mNextTime = t + mRate;
51  mData.push_back(v);
52  } else if (delta > -.5 * mRate) {
53  mData.push_back(v);
54  mNextTime = t + mRate;
55  } else {
56  LogDebug(2, "Data ignored");
57  }
58  }

66  void ChannelDescriptor::PushFrVect(FrVect *frv, double t, unsigned int off, double offset, double slope) {
67 
68  switch (frv->type) {
69  case FR_VECT_C:
70  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
71  Queue((double) (frv->data[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
72  }
73  break;
74  case FR_VECT_2S:
75  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
76  Queue((double) (frv->dataS[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
77  }
78  break;
79  case FR_VECT_4S:
80  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
81  Queue((double) (frv->dataI[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
82  }
83  break;
84  case FR_VECT_8S:
85  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
86  Queue((double) (frv->dataL[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
87  }
88  break;
89  case FR_VECT_1U:
90  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
91  Queue((double) (frv->dataU[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
92  }
93  break;
94  case FR_VECT_2U:
95  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
96  Queue((double) (frv->dataUS[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
97  }
98  break;
99  case FR_VECT_4U:
100  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
101  Queue((double) (frv->dataUI[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
102  }
103  break;
104  case FR_VECT_8U:
105  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
106  Queue((double) (frv->dataUL[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
107  }
108  break;
109  case FR_VECT_4R:
110  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
111  Queue((double) (frv->dataF[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
112  }
113  break;
114  case FR_VECT_8R:
115  for (unsigned int i = off; i < frv->nData; i++) {
116  Queue((double) (frv->dataD[ i ]) * slope + offset, t + mRate * i);
117  }
118  break;
119  default:
120  LogSevere("FrVectCopy: unknown type");
121  throw std::runtime_error("ChannelDescriptor::PushFrVect - unknown type");
122  }
123  }

125  bool ChannelDescriptor::data_available(double t) {
126  if (mExceptions.size() == 0) {
127  return true;
128  }
129  switch (mExceptions.front().Exception) {
130  case DataException::data_loss:
131  if ((t >= mExceptions.front().StartTime)) {
132 
133  if (t < mExceptions.front().EndTime) {
134  return false;
135  }
136 
137  mExceptions.pop_front();
138  return data_available(t);
139 
140  } else {
141  return true;
142  }
143  break;
144  default:
145  throw std::runtime_error("Unimplemented data exception");
146  }
147  }

149  void ChannelDescriptor::WriteView(SeqViewDouble& v) {
150  //Dmatrix* d = &Attribute<Dmatrix>(v,"Data");
151  Dmatrix* d = v.GetData();
152  v.SetStart(mFIS->GetStartTime());
153  v.SetSampling(mRate);
154  v.SetScale(1.0);
155 
156  double tl = mFIS->GetTimeLength();
157  unsigned int n = (unsigned int) floor(tl / mRate);
158 
159  if ((d->size1() != 1) || (d->size2() != n)) {
160  d->resize(1, n);
161  }
162 
163  double tm = mFIS->GetStartTime();
164  for (unsigned int k = 0; k < n; k++) {
165  if (data_available(tm)) {
166  (*d)(0, k) = mData.front();
167  mData.pop_front();
168  } else {
169  (*d)(0, k) = 0.0;
170  mFIS->SetDataLossFlag(true);
171  }
172  tm += mRate;
173  }
174  }

531  void FRAMEH_Channel::AddData() {

533 
534  switch (mFieldType) {
535  case field_run:
536  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->run);
537  break;
538  case field_frame:
539  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->frame);
540  break;
541  case field_dataQuality:
542  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->dataQuality);
543  break;
544  case field_GTimeS:
545  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeS);
546  break;
547  case field_GTimeN:
548  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeN);
549  break;

551  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->ULeapS);
552  break;
553  case field_dt:
554  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->dt);
555  break;
556  case field_time:
557  value = double(mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeS + 1e-9 * mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeN);
558  break;
559  default:
560  break;
561  }
562  double tstart = mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeS + mFIS->GetFrame()->GTimeN * 1.0e9;
563  PushValue(value, tstart, 1);
564  LogDebug(3, "Data now: %d (%f seconds)", mData.size(), mRate * mData.size());

606  void FrameIStream::Init() {
607  // Open the frame file
608  mpFrameFile = FrFileINew(const_cast<char *> (mFileName.c_str()));
609  if (mpFrameFile == NULL) {
610  std::stringstream s;
611  s << "File " << mFileName << " open error";
612  std::string emsg = s.str();
613  LogSevere("%s", emsg.c_str());
614  throw std::runtime_error(emsg);
615  } else {
616  LogDebug(3, "File %s opened", mFileName.c_str());
617  }
618 
619  // Try to get the first frame using TOC
620  mpFrame = FrameReadT(mpFrameFile, mStartTime);
621  if (mpFrame == NULL) {
622  // Find the first frame without TOC
623  mpFrame = FrameRead(mpFrameFile);
624  if (mpFrame == NULL) {
625  std::stringstream s;
626  s << "No frames inside file " << mFileName;
627  std::string emsg = s.str();
628  LogSevere("%s", emsg.c_str());
629  throw std::runtime_error(emsg);
630  }
631  if (mpFrame->GTimeS > mStartTime) {
632  std::stringstream s;
633  s << "No frames at the given time inside file " << mFileName;
634  std::string emsg = s.str();
635  LogSevere("%s", emsg.c_str());
636  throw std::runtime_error(emsg);
637  }
638  while (mpFrame->GTimeS + mpFrame->dt < mStartTime) {
639  FrameFree(mpFrame);
640  mpFrame = FrameRead(mpFrameFile);
641  if (mpFrame == NULL) {
642  std::stringstream s;
643  s << "No frames a the given time inside file " << mFileName;
644  std::string emsg = s.str();
645  LogSevere("%s", emsg.c_str());
646  throw std::runtime_error(emsg);
647  }
648  }
649  LogDebug(3, "FrameRead: got frame starting at %f", mpFrame->GTimeS);
650  } else {
